Supports a wide variety of map formats: orthogonal, isometric, and hexagonal.
Features an intuitive user interface for easy tile placement and design.
Highly flexible with JSON, Lua, and XML export options for easy integration into custom engines.
Open-source with an active community and plugin support.
Compatible with a variety of game engines, including Godot, Unity, and Cocos.
Supports tile animations and terrain blending for more dynamic levels.

Website: https://www.mapeditor.org
